                                 </li>
                         
                                 <!-- data rows -->
                                 <li class="row_style_3 align_center"><span>Cut can make a diamond look bigger. It means that you get a free boost in the other aspects of the 3Cs (color, carat and clarity) just by having a better cut.</span></li>
                                 <li class="row_style_1 align_center"><span>The cut of a diamond refers not only to the shape of the diamond and number of facets, but also to the quality of the cut. </span></li>
                           
                              </ul>
