                                    <h2 class="col3">Carat</h2>
                                 </li>
               
                                 <!-- data rows -->
                                 <li class="row_style_3 align_center"><span>Carat is used to describe the weight of diamonds. Generally the larger the stone the greater value. Diamond carat weight is the measurement of how much a diamond weighs.</span></li>
                                 <li class="row_style_1 align_center"><span>Each carat can be subdivided into 100 'points.' This allows very precise measurements to the hundredth decimal place.</span></li>

                                
                              </ul>
                           </div>
