                                 </li>

                                 <!-- data rows -->
                                 <li class="row_style_4 align_center"><span>Clarity measures the imperfections. The purest, the higher its value. GIA considers the number, size, color, reflectivity, and position of every flaw visible under 10x magnification.</span></li>
                                 <li class="row_style_2 align_center"><span> In a certified diamond, the cracks are charted on the certificate and act as a fingerprint for identifying a particular stone.</span></li>
                                 
                                
